Bigger cheques, fewer deals: What’s driving India’s startup revival? 
Deal value is on the mend as well, and that's despite lower volumes. While 2024 saw early-stage startups raise $1.5 billion across 513 deals, this year so far has seen 432 deals with companies raising a total of $1.6 billion.&nbsp; 
